{"id": 3220, "title": "Ticket #3220: Allow different submit limits for grid resources", "description": "<blockquote>\nMany groups would like to be able to set different job submission limits (i.e. GRIDMANAGER_MAX_SUBMITTED_JOBS_PER_RESOURCE) for different remote servers. There is code in the gridmanager to allow this, but it's been broken for a long time. We could get it working pretty easily.\n\n<p>The revived old syntax works like this:\n</p><div class=\"code\">\n<pre class=\"code\">GRIDMANAGER_MAX_SUBMITTED_JOBS_PER_RESOURCE=5,foo.edu,10,bar.org,15\n</pre></div>\n\n\n<p>It's a comma-separated list. The first entry is the default limit. Each subsequent pair of entries are a hostname and the limit for that hostname. The gridmanager does a substring match of the hostname field against the name returned by BaseResource::ResourceName(). ResourceName() returns a modified form of the second field of the <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=GridResource\" title=\"Grid Resource\">GridResource</a></span> attribute.</p></blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n<hr/>\n<em>2012-Oct-22 14:59:59 by zmiller:</em> <br/>\n\nBulk change of target version from v070901 to v070902 using ./ticket-target-mover.</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Oct-31 15:20</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/d20657d9d6ca4107ad784b25ea327f3974f04f25\">[33953]</a></span>: clarify some knob definitions added/changed for 7.9.1 ===GT=== <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3220\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3220'); return false;\" title=\"Allow different submit limits for grid resources\">#3220</a></span>  (By Karen Miller )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Oct-22 14:58</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/e348801aac76cbe07de0e6fe6467cef600383d87\">[33736]</a></span>: Update manual for gridmanager config params changes. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3220\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3220'); return false;\" title=\"Allow different submit limits for grid resources\">#3220</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3023\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3023'); return false;\" title=\"Configurable poll intervals for Condor-G based on number of jobs\">#3023</a></span>  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\n<tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2012-Oct-22 11:19</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"https://github.com/htcondor/htcondor/commit/f6dc31178ec024afc5813c77a2c3e7c0cb80c1b1\">[33726]</a></span>: version history updates <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3039\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3039'); return false;\" title=\"get file transfer remaps working for directories\">#3039</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=3129\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('3129'); return false;\" title=\"Have schedd dynamically spawn local startd\">#3129</a></span> <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/wiki-archive/tickets/?ticket=2366\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2366'); return false;\"